title: Cant Que due to "difference in rank" but same rank as duo partner
body:
Title
Me and my friend was wanting to duo que. Both are gold 3, but won't let us que due to our ranks being too high.

replies.body: Do you ranks match in the same queue? That's about the only reason I can think that would be occurring. If you're playing solo//duo it'll pull your ranks from solo/duo, not from flex or whatever other queues you may be ranked in.
